9","tid":2498322,"uid":254191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"507e51649f285e1a84d2a2bca9366770b5731f33","tid":2498322,"uid":397478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9a7922689e3ccd121a1bfdbedef44d58edd78db","tid":2498322,"uid":254191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"自己睇jd啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:16:47.000Z","msg":"JD好複雜 睇唔明<br />\n係想知有係哩個項目做噶同事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"放上黎大家一齊研究<br />\n就咁聽個名似it"},{"pid":"7a64ac020dc75de7cb57cbfc99164e265d675ebc","tid":2498322,"uid":397478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78cf2b4de816525e516c2a60e3f14399f98a6449","tid":2498322,"uid":254191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"507e51649f285e1a84d2a2bca9366770b5731f33","tid":2498322,"uid":397478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9a7922689e3ccd121a1bfdbedef44d58edd78db","tid":2498322,"uid":254191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"自己睇jd啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:16:47.000Z","msg":"JD好複雜 睇唔明<br />\n係想知有係哩個項目做噶同事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"放上黎大家一齊研究<br />\n就咁聽個名似it"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"Corporate Sales Trainee<br />\nIn this position, you will:<br />\nGenerate new business by offering consultation to corporate clients on data solutions and Telecommunications services (e.g. leased line, broadband services, ICT products)<br />\nDevelop accounts through strategic based selling and relationship management strategic accounts<br />\nMaintain and analyze client profiles for better segmenting and targeting<br />\nEngage clients by delivering sales presentations and preparing business proposals in a professional manner<br />\nPrepare sales reports and forecast business trend to achieve budgeted sales objectives<br />\n<br />\nPresales Support Trainee<br />\nIn this position, you will:<br />\nObtain and review client&rsquo;s requirements as to propose the best-fit solutions to fulfill client&rsquo;s needs<br />\nAct as a liaison between the IT and business community to make sure the proposed technology can meet the project goals<br />\nWork with external partners and internal departments and line of business to formulate solution proposal<br />\nRespond to RFI / tender and responsible for solution and technical write-up, translation of functional and non-functional requirements into a solution design and Scope of Work<br />\nSource vendors and obtain quotations to meet the customers&rsquo; budgets<br />\nPrepare and deliver demonstration / presentation to customers and partners<br />\n&nbsp;To be a successful candidate for this program, you should meet the following requirements:<br />\nDegree or above, major in Business Administration, IT, Engineering or related disciplines.<br />\nFresh graduate or degree graduate with no more than 1-year working experience<br />\nStrong passion for sales / telecom field<br />\nKnowledge in ICT products/ technologies would be an advantage<br />\nResult-oriented, self-motivated with strong desire to succeed and willing to take up challenges<br />\nExcellent communication, interpersonal and presentation skills<br />\nGood command of both spoken and written English and Chinese, with the knowledge of Putonghua is preferable"},{"pid":"ae760be637d144333037e4b3ab5c10fef12fca4d","tid":2498322,"uid":397478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ff71a5a6960b59d8d2a2e11a345bd81b6d020e8","tid":2498322,"uid":75487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"Deal咗Viu再傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"